{"tid":1889564,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"想問ebay refund點做？","createTime":"2020-02-20T16:39:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T09:19:57.000Z","uid":39703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f63b6abd2d1972a71059b13be705f3bc42bfa835","tid":1889564,"uid":39703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T16:39:13.000Z","msg":"話說一月尾係ebay買口罩  用信用卡俾左錢<br />\n個賣家話7/2-17/2會寄到<br />\n但遲遲都未話shipped <br />\nSend過email問佢幾時ship都冇回覆<br />\n<br />\n前日終於send個request cancellation 俾我話冇貨<br />\n我可以揀接受/不接受<br />\n但接受個選擇下面寫「只有在未付款/賣家已退款情況下才接受取消交易要求」<br />\n然後我再Email佢叫佢refund先<br />\n點知佢覆我話佢地Refund唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以先要request cancellation 話我接受左ebay先會幫我refund<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSend左email俾ebay兩次都冇覆<br />\n想點下其實ebay點refund <br />\n<br />\n利申 同左銀行溝通 佢地會幫我跟進"},{"pid":"92287c2476b8c8945d27c24b75d6333da11902a3","tid":1889564,"uid":68598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T16:40:35.000Z","msg":"用paypal俾錢就打俾PayPal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快好多"},{"pid":"3b704cf84d3741397734d32c63865a91b92249ea","tid":1889564,"uid":39703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92287c2476b8c8945d27c24b75d6333da11902a3","tid":1889564,"uid":68598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T16:40:35.000Z","msg":"用paypal俾錢就打俾PayPal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />快好多"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T16:46:51.000Z","msg":"Not paypal啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/